### 좋아요 등록 - 성공 케이스 (사전: 회원가입 + 상품 등록 필요)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/products/1/likes
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser1
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Test1234!

### 좋아요 등록 - 이미 좋아요한 상품 (실패, 409 CONFLICT)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/products/1/likes
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser1
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Test1234!

### 좋아요 등록 - 존재하지 않는 상품 (실패, 404 NOT_FOUND)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/products/999/likes
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser1
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Test1234!

### 좋아요 등록 - 인증 헤더 누락 (실패, 401 UNAUTHORIZED)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/products/1/likes

### 좋아요 등록 - 잘못된 비밀번호 (실패, 401 UNAUTHORIZED)
POST {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/products/1/likes
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser1
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Wrong1234!

