X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser1
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Test1234!

### 좋아요 취소 - 인증 헤더 누락 (실패, 401 UNAUTHORIZED)
DELETE {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/products/1/likes

### 좋아요 취소 - 잘못된 비밀번호 (실패, 401 UNAUTHORIZED)
DELETE {{commerce-api}}/api/v1/products/1/likes
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser1
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Wrong1234!

